job.title: RSMSSB Agriculture Supervisor Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 2254 Vacancies in Rajasthan
job.body:
Total vacancies:2254

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Agriculture Supervisor

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for 10+2 passes have been published by Rajasthan Subordinate and Ministerial Services Selection Board for Agriculture Supervisor vacancies in Rajasthan. If you are searching for a government job in Rajasthan then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Agriculture Supervisor, from 08-07-2021, and till 22-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Rajasthan and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for GEN/ OBC Creamy Layer category candidates is only Rs. 450/-
  • The application fee for BC/ OBC Non-Creamy Layer category candidates is only Rs. 350/-
  • The application fee for SC/ ST Candidates category candidates is only Rs. 250/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for an Agriculture Supervisor in RSMSSB, your 10+2 Intermediate in Agriculture Stream with B.Sc (Agriculture) must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 08-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 22-07-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40 years old. 

RSMSSB Agriculture Supervisor Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for RSMSSB Agriculture Supervisor Recruitment 2021?

 Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Agriculture Supervisor. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of RSMSSB and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by RSMSSB.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
